OL,15,Fscarlet fever have led to a surge in
OL,16,Fdemand for penicillin and other
OL,17,Fantibiotics, with shortages reported by
OL,18,Fmany pharmacies across the country `
OL,19,Fincluding one family who reportedly had
OL,20,Fto travel 20 miles with a prescription.
